1: lrn_mode=lrn_skip
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Configures handling of IP multicast routing on stack link.

If IP multicast routing is performed in egress unit, then routed copies shall not be forwarded on the stack ports and this parameter must thus be set to 0.

If IP multicast routing is performed in ingress unit (or centralized), then routed copies shall be forwarded on the stack ports and this parameter must thus be set to 3.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
0: Disable multicast on both links
1: Enable multicast routing on stack link A
2: Enable multicast routing on stack link B
