<reggrp_short_dscr>:
Source port masks
------------------------------
<reggrp_public_text>:
Source port masks per inbound front port number (index 0 to 70-1) and per source GLAG (index: 70 to 102-1).

Source port masks for GLAGs are offset by number of inbound ports.

To avoid forwarding back to another LLAG member port, ports that are part of the same LLAG must be disabled in the port masks for all LLAG member ports. 

The source port masks for front ports are initialized to "walking zero".
The source port masks for the GLAGs are initialized to all-ones.
