<reg_short_dscr>:
PTP Domain select for Stream Gates
------------------------------
<reg_public_text>:
The Stream Gates uses PTP timing as the reference time for all Gate Open / Close operations. For this to work, Stream Gates must be configured for which PTP time domain to use. There are 4 time domains in chip and the register must be configured in range  0-3 to be associated to one of the PTP time domain.
