<reg_short_dscr>:
Configures how often Stream Gates Cycle Timer update must be done
------------------------------
<reg_public_text>:
The SetCycleStartTime() must be run periodically for all active Stream Gates, so that the Cycle Start Time must remain within 1 CycleTime of current time. The recommended value is 10us converted in System clocks. This implies that minimum value of CycleTime for any active stream gate supported by chip is 10us. Lower values of CycleTime can also be supported by reducing the time between period update.
